hadiths[132]{hadithnumber,text}:
603,(namaz ke waqt ke elaan ke liye) logon ne aag aur naaqoos ka zikr kya. phir yahood w nasara ka zikr aa gaya. phir Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye hukm hua ke azan ke kalimaat 2-2 martaba kahin aur iqamat mein eik-eik martaba.
604,"jab musalman ( hijrat karke ( Madina pahunchey to waqt muqarrar karke Namaz ke liye aatey they. uske liye azan nahi di jati thi. aik din us barey mein mashwara hua. kisi ne kaha nasara ki tarah aik ghanta ley liya jaey aur kisi ne kaha ke yahudiyon ki tarah narsingha (bigul bana lo, usko phoonk diya karo) lekin umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke kisi shakhs ko kyon na bhej diya jaey jo Namaz ke liye pukar diya kare. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (usi raey ko pasand farmaya aur Bilal se) farmaya ke Bilaal! uth aur Namaz ke liye azan de."
605,Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya gaya ke azan ke kalimaat 2-2 martaba kahin aur siwa (qad qaamatissalaat) ke takbeer ke kalimaat eik-eik baar kahein.
606,jab musalman zyada ho gaey to mashwara hua ke kisi aisi cheez ke zariey Namaz ke waqt ka elaan ho jisey sab log samajh lein. kuchh logon ne zikr kya ke aag roshan ki jaey. ya narsingha ke zariey elaan karein. lekin aakhir mein Bilal ko hukm diya gaya ke azan ke kalimaat 2-2 baar kahein aur takbeer ke eik-eik baar.
607,Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya gaya ke azan ke kalimaat 2-2 baar kahein aur takbeer mein yahi kalimaat eik-eik baar. Ismail ne bataya ke maine Ayub sakhtiyan se us hadis ka zikr kya to unhon-ne kaha magar lafz (qad qaamatissalaat) 2 hi baar kaha jaeyga
608,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jab Namaz ke ke liye azan di jati hai to shaitan paadta (hawa khaarij karta) hua badi tezi ke sath peeth mod kar bhaagta hai. taake azan ki awaz na sun sakey aur jab azan khatm ho jati hai to phir wapas aa jata hai. lekin joon hi takbeer shuru hui wo phir peeth mod kar bhaagta hai. jab takbeer bhi khatm ho jati hai to shaitan dobara aa jata hai aur namazi ke dil mein waswasey daalta hai. kehta hai ke falan baat yad kar falan baat yad kar. un baton ki shaitan yad dahaanii karaataa hai jinka usey khayal bhi na tha aur is tarah us shakhs ko ye bhi yad nahi rehta ke usne kitni rakatein padhi hain.
609,mein dekhta hun ke tumhen bakriyon aur jangal mein rehna pasand hai. isliye jab tum jangal main apni bakriyon ko liye huey maujood ho aur Namaz ke liye azan 2 to tum buland awaz se azan diya karo. kyonke jin w insan balke tamam hi cheezein jo muazzan ki awaz suntii hain qiyamat ke din is par gawahi dengii. abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke ye maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai.
610,"jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamein sath lekar kahin jihad ke liye tashrif ley jatey, to fauran hi hamla nahi kartey they. subah hoti aur phir aap intizar kartey agar azan ki awaz sun letey to hamle ka irada tark kar detey aur agar azan ki awaz na sunai deti to hamla kartey they. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ham khaibar ki taraf gaey aur raat ke waqt wahan pahunchey. subah ke waqt jab azan ki awaz nahi sunai di to aap apni sawari par baith gaey aur main abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ke peechhey baith gaya. chalney mein mere qadam Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qadam Mubarak se chhu chhu jatey they. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Khaibar ke log apne tokron aur kudaalon ko liye huey (apne kaam kaaj ko) bahar nikley. to unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha, aur chilla uthey ke ''(Muhammad Allah ki qism Muhammad!) (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) poori fauj samet aa gaey.'' Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein dekha to aap ne farmaya (الله أكبر ,‏‏‏‏‏‏ الله أكبر ( khaibar par kharabi aa gaee. beshak jab ham kisi qaum ke maidan mein utar jayen to un logon ki subah buri hogi jinhein daraaya gaya tha."
611,ke jab tum azan suno to jis tarah muazzan kehta hai isi tarah tum bhi kaho.
612,"unhon-ne Muawiya bin abi Sufiyan se aik din suna aap ( jawab mein) muazzan ke hi alfaz ko dohra rahe they. أشهد أن محمدا رسول الله tak. ham se Ishaq bin Raaviya ne bayan kya, kaha ke ham se Wahab-bin-Jareer ne bayan kya, kaha ke ham se Hisham dustwaai ne Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir se isi tarah hadis bayan ki."
613,jab muazzan ne  حى على الصلاة kahaa to Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne لا حول wla قوة إلا بالله‏ kahaa aur kehney lagey ke ham ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aisa hi kehtey suna hai.
614,jo shakhs azan sun kar ye kahey اللهم رب هذه الدعوة التامة والصلاة القائمة آت محمدا الوسيلة والفضيلة وابعثه مقاما محمودا الذي وعدته usey qiyamat ke din meri shafaat milegii.
615,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar logon ko malum hota ke azan kehney aur Namaz pehli saf mein padhney se kitna sawab milta hai. phir unke liye Qura dalney ke siwaey aur koi chaara nahi baqi rehta, to albatta is par Qura andazi hi kartey aur agar logon ko malum ho jata ke Namaz ke liye jaldi aaney mein kitna sawab milta hai to uske liye doosrey se aagey badhney ki koshish kartey aur agar logon ko malum ho jata ke isha aur subah ki Namaz ka sawab kitna milta hai, to zaroor koolhon ke bal ghaseet'tey huey unke liye aatey."
616,"Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne aik din ham ko Juma ka khutba diya. barish ki wjah se us din achi khasi keechad ho rahi thi. muazzan jab حى على الصلاة‏ par pahuncha to aap ne us se ( الصلاة في الرحال‏ ( kehney ke liye farmaya ke log Namaz apni qiyam gaahon par padh lein. is par log aik doosrey ko dekhney lagey. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke isi tarah mujh se jo afzal they, unhon-ne bhi kya tha aur is mein shak nahi ke Juma wajib hai."
617,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Bilal to raat rahe azan detey hain. isliye tum log khaatey peetey raho. yahan tak ke ibne-umme-Maktoom azan dein. rawi ne kaha ke wo naa-beenaa they aur us waqt tak azan nahi detey they jab tak unse kaha na jata ke subah ho gaee. subah ho gaee.
618,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aadat thi ke jab muazzan subah ki azan subah sadiq ke tuloo honey ke baad de chuka hota to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) azan aur takbeer ke beech Namaz qaaim honey se pahley 2 halki si rakatein padhtey.
619,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) fajr ki azan aur iqamat ke darmyan 2 halki si rakatein padhtey they.
620,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, dekho Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) raat rahe mein azan detey hain, isliye tum log (sehrii) kha pi saktey ho. jab tak ibne-umme-maktoom azan na dein."
621,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Bilal ki azan tumhen sehrii khaney se na rok de kyonke wo raat rahe se azan detey hain ya (ye kaha ke) pukaartey hain. taake jo log ibadat ke liye jaagey hain wo aaraam karne ke liye lot jayen aur jo abhi soey huey hain wo hoshiyaar ho jaaein. koi ye na samajh baithey ke fajr ya subah sadiq ho gaee aur aap ne apni ungliyon ke ishaarey se (tulooa' subah ki kaifiyat) bataaii. ungliyon ko uper ki taraf uthaya aur phir aahista se unhein nichey laey aur phir farmaya ke is tarah (fajr hoti hai) Zuhair rawi ne bhi shahadat ki ungli aik dusri par rakhii, phir unhein daain-baaiin taraf phaila diya."
622,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya (Bilaal raat rahe mein azan detey hain. Abdullah ibne-umme-Maktoom ki azan tak tum (sehrii) kha pi saktey ho).
623,Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Bilal raat rahe mein azan detey hain. Abdullaah-ibne-umme-Maktoom ki azan tak tum ( sehrii ( kha pi saktey ho.
624,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne teen martaba farmaya ke har 2 azaanon (azaan w iqaamat) ke darmyan aik Namaz (ka fasl) dusri Namaz se hona chahiye ( teesri martaba farmaya ke) jo shakhs aisa karna chaahey.
625,aap ne farmaya ke (ahde-risaalat mein) jab muazzan azan deta to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba sutunon ki taraf lapaktey. jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne hujre se bahar tashrif latey to log isi tarah Namaz padhtey huey miltey. ye jamat maghrib se pahley ki 2 rakatein thin aur (maghrib mein) azan aur takbeer mein koi zyada fasla nahi hota tha aur Usmaan-bin-jabla aur Abu-Dawud Tiyalisi ne Shoba se us (hadees mein yun naql kya hai ke) azan aur takbeer mein bahut thoda sa fasla hota tha.
626,jab muazzan subah ki dusri azan de kar chup hota to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey hotey aur farz se pahley 2 rakaat ( sunnat fajr ( halki phulkii ada kartey subah sadiq roshan ho janey ke baad phir dahini karwat par let rehtey. yahan tak ke muazzan takbeer kehney ki itlaa dene ke liye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aataa.
627,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke har 2 azaanon ( azan w takbeer (ke beech mein Namaz hai. har 2 azaanon ke darmyan Namaz hai. phir teesri martaba Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar koi padhna chaahey.
628,main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat main apni qaum ( bani Leis (ke chand aadmiyon ke sath hazir hua aur maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat sharif mein bees raaton tak qiyam kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) badey raham dil aur milansaar they. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamarey apne ghar pahunchne ka shauq mehsus kar liya to farmaya ke ab tum ja saktey ho. wahan ja kar apni qaum ko Deen sikhaao aur (safar mein) Namaz padhtey rehna. jab Namaz ka waqt aa jaey to tum mein se aik shakhs azan de aur jo tum mein sabse bada ho wo imamat karaaey.
629,ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik safar mein they. muazzan ne azan deeni chahi to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya thanda honey de. phir muazzan ne azan deeni chahi to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir yahi farmaya ke thanda honey de. yahan tak ke saaya teelon ke barabar ho gaya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke garmi ki shiddat dozakh ki bhap se paida hoti hai.
630,"2 log Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaey ye kisi safar mein janey waley they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke dekho jab tum safar mein niklo to (namaz ke waqt rastey mein) azan dena phir iqamat kehna , phir jo shakhs tum mein umr mein bada ho Namaz padhaaey ."
631,ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey. ham sab ham umr aur naujawaan hi they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hamara bees din w raat qiyam raha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) badey hi raham dil aur milansaar they. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dekha ke hamein apne watan wapas janey ka shauq hai to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha ke tum log apne ghar kisey chhod kar aaey ho. ham ne bataya. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke achchha ab tum apne ghar jao aur un ghar walon ke sath raho aur unhein bhi Deen sikhaao aur Deen ki baton par amal karne ka hukm karo. Malik ne bahut si chizon ka zikr kya jinke mutaalliq Abu-Ayub ne kaha ke abu-Qilaba ne yun kaha wo baatein mujh ko yad hain ya yun kaha mujh ko yad nahi. aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke isi tarah Namaz padhna jaisey tum ne mujhey Namaz padhtey huey dekha hai aur jab Namaz ka waqt aa jaey to koi aik azan de aur jo tum mein sabse bada ho wo Namaz padhaaey.
632,Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne aik sard raat mein maqam Zajnaan par azan di phir farmaayaa ألا صلوا في الرحال ke logo! apne-apney thikaanon mein Namaz padh lo aur hamein aap ne batlaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) muazzan se azan ke liye farmatey aur ye bhi farmatey ke muazzan azan ke baad keh de ke logo! apne thikaanon mein Namaz padh lo. ye hukm safar ki haalat mein ya sardi ya barsat ki raaton mein tha.
633,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Abtah mein dekha ke Bilal hazir huey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Namaz ki khabar di phir Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) barchhi lekar aagey badhey aur usey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney (bataur sutrah) maqaame-abtah mein gaad diya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( usko satrah bana kar) Namaz padhai.
634,unhon-ne Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko azan detey huey dekha. wo kehtey hain mein bhi unke munh ke sath idhar-udhar munh pherney laga.
635,"ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Namaz mein they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kuchh logon ke chalney phirney aur bolney ki awaz suni. Namaz ke baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke kya qissa hai logon ne kaha ke ham Namaz ke liye jaldi kar rahe they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aisa na karo. balke jab tum Namaz ke liye aao to waqaar aur sukoon rakho, Namaz ka jo hissey paogey usey padho aur aur jo reh jaey usey ( baad) mein pura kar lo."
636,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tum log takbeer ki awaz sun lo to Namaz ke liye (ma'moolii chaal se) chal pado. sukoon aur waqaar ko (bahar-haal) pakdey rakho aur daud ke mat aao. phir Namaz ka jo hissey miley usey padh lo, aur jo na mil sakey usey baad mein pura kar lo."
637,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab Namaz ke liye takbeer kahi jaey to us waqt tak na khadey ho jab tak mujhey nikaltey huey na dekh lo.
638,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Namaz ki takbeer ho to jab tak mujhey dekh na lo khadey na ho aur aahisatagi ko lazim rakho. Sheban ke sath us hadis ko Yahya se Ali bin-Mubarak ne bhi riwayat kya hai.
639,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (eik din hujrey se) bahar tashrif laaey, iqamat kahi ja chuki thi aur safein barabar ki ja chuki thin. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab musalley par khadey huey to ham intizar kar rahe they ke ab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) takbeer kehtey hain. lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wapas tashrif le gaey aur farmaya ke apni apni jagah par thahrey raho. ham usi haalat mein thahrey rahe yahan tak ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) dobara tashrif laaey, to sar Mubarak se pani tapak raha tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ghusl kya tha."
640,Namaz ke liye iqamat kahi ja chuki thi aur logon ne safein seedhi kar li thin. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey aur aagey badhey. lekin haalate-janaabat mein they ( magar pahley khayal na raha ( isliye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum log apni apni jagah thahrey raho. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wapas tashrif laey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghusl kiye huey they aur sar Mubarak se pani tapak raha tha. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne logon ko Namaz padhai.
641,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) Khandaq ki jang ke din hazir huey aur kaha ya Rasulullah ! qism Allah ki suraj ghurub honey ko hi tha ke main ab Asr ki Namaz padh saka hun. aap jab haazire-khidmat huey to roza iftaar karne ka waqt aa chuka tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke qism Allah ki maine bhi to namaze-Asr nahi padhi hai. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Bathaan ki taraf gaey. mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath hi tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wuzu kya, phir Asr ki Namaz padhi. suraj doob chuka tha. phir iske baad maghrib ki Namaz padhi."
642,Namaz ke liye takbeer ho chuki thi aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kisi shakhs se masjid ke aik goshey mein chupkey chupkey kaan mein baatein kar rahe they. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz ke liye jab tashrif laey to log so rahe they.
643,maine Sabit Bunani se aik shakhs ke mutaalliq masla malum kya jo Namaz ke liye takbeer honey ke baad guftgu karta rahe. is par unhon-ne Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kya ke unhon-ne farmaya ke takbeer ho chuki thi. itney mein aik shakhs Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se raaste mein mila aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Namaz ke liye takbeer kahi janey ke baad bhi rokey rakha.
644,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai maine irada kar liya tha ke lakdiyon ke jama karne ka hukm dun. phir Namaz ke liye kahoon, uske liye azan di jaey phir kisi shakhs se kahun ke wo imamat karey aur main un logon ki taraf jaun (jo Namaz ba-jamaat mein hazir nahi hotey ( phir unhein unke gharon samet jalaa dun. us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai agar ye jamat mein na Sharik hone-waale log itni baat jaan lein ke unhein masjid mein aik achchhey qism ki gosht wali haddi mil jaeygi ya 2 umda khur hi mil jaeinge to ye isha ki jamat ke liye masjid mein zaroor hazir ho jaaein."
645,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jamat ke sath Namaz akeley Namaz padhney se sattais darja zyada fazeelat rakhti hai.
646,Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey they ke jamat se Namaz tanha Namaz padhney se pachchis darja zyada fazeelat rakhti hai.
647,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aadmi ki jamat ke sath Namaz ghar mein ya bazar mein padhney se pachchis darja zyada behtar hai. wjah ye hai ke jab aik shakhs wuzu karta hai aur uske tamam aadaab ko malhooz rakh kar achi tarah wuzu karta hai phir masjid ka rasta pakadta hai aur siwa Namaz ke aur koi doosra irada uska nahi hota, to har qadam par uska aik darja badhtaa hai aur aik gunah maaf kya jata hai aur jab Namaz se farigh ho jata hai to Farishtey us waqt tak uske liye barabar duaein kartey rahtey hain jab tak wo apne musalley par betha rahe. kehtey hain ( اللهم صل عليه ‏‏‏‏ اللهم ارحمه‏ ) aey Allah ! is par apni rahmatein nazil farmaa. aey Allah ! is par raham kar aur jab tak tum Namaz ka intizar kartey raho maano tum Namaz hi mein mashghool ho."
648,Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jamat se Namaz akeley padhney se pachchis darja zyada behtar hai. aur raat din ke Farishtey fajr ki Namaz mein jama hotey hain. phir Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke agar tum padhna chaho to (Sura banii-Israaeel) ki ye aayat padho (إن قرآن الفجر كان مشهودا‏ ) yani fajr mein Quran paak ki tilawat par Farishtey hazir hotey hain.
649,jamat ki Namaz akeley ki Namaz se sattais darja zyada fazeelat rakhti hai.
650,"(eik martaba ( abu-Darda aaey, badey hi khafa ho rahe they. maine puchha ke kya baat hui, jisne aapko ghazabnaak bana diya. farmaya : Allah ki qism ! Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki shariiat ki koi baat ab main nahi paata. siwa iske ke jamat ke sath ye log Namaz padh letey hain."
651,"Namaz mein sawab ke lihaaz se sabse badh kar wo shakhs hota hai, jo (masjid mein Namaz ke liye) zyada se zyada door se aaey aur jo shakhs Namaz ke intizar mein betha rehta hai aur phir imam ke sath padhta hai us shakhs se ajr mein badh kar hai jo (pahley hi ( padh kar so jaey."
652,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya aik shakhs kahin ja raha tha. rastey mein usne kaanton ki bhari hui aik tahnii dekhi, to usey rastey se door kar diya. Allah Taala ( sirf isi baat par) razi ho gaya aur uski bakhshish kar dii.`"
653,"shohdaa panch qism ke hotey hain. taaoon mein marney waale, pet ki beemaari (haizey wghaira) mein marney waley aur doob kar marney waley aur jo diwar wghaira kisi bhi cheez se dab kar mar jaey aur Allah ke rastey mein (jihad kartey huey) Shahid hone-waale aur aap ne farmaya ke agar logon ko malum ho jaey ke azan dene aur pehli saf mein Sharik honey ka sawab kitna hai aur phir iske siwa koi chaara kaar na ho ke Qura daala jaey to log unke liye Qura hi daala karein."
654,"aur agar logon ko ye malum ho jaey ke Zohar ki Namaz ke liye sawerey janey mein kya sawab hai to uske liye aik doosrey par pahal karne ki koshish karein aur agar ye jaan jayen ke isha aur subah ki Namaz ke fazaail kitney hain, to ghutnon ke bal ghisattey huey unke liye aaein."
655,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, aey banu- Salma waalo! kya tum apne qadmon ka sawab nahi chaahtey?"
656,"mujhey Yahya bin Ayub ne khabar di, kaha ke mujh se Humaid lamba ne bayan kya, kaha ke mujh se Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke banu-Salma walon ne ye irada kya ke apne makan (jo masjid se door they) chhod dein aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qareeb aa rahen. (taake ba-jamaat ke liye masjide-Nabawi ka sawab hasil ho) lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Madina ka ujaad dena bura malum hua. aap ne farmaya ke tum log apne qadmon ka sawab nahi chaahtey? Mujahid ne kaha ( sura Yasin mein) ( وآثارهم ( se qadam murad hain. yani zameen par chalney se paon ke nishaanaat."
657,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke munaafiqon par fajr aur isha ki Namaz se zyada aur koi Namaz bhari nahi aur agar unhein malum hota ke unka sawab kitna zyada hai (aur chal na saktey) to ghutnon ke bal ghaseet kar aatey aur mera to irada ho gaya tha ke muazzan se kahun ke wo takbeer kahey, phir main kisi ko Namaz padhaaney ke liye kahun aur khud aag ki chingaariyaan lekar un sab ke gharon ko jalaa dun jo abhi tak Namaz ke liye nahi nikley."
658,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jab Namaz ka waqt aa jaey to tum donon azan 2 aur iqamat kaho, phir jo tum mein bada hai wo imam baney."
659,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke malaaika tum mein se us namazi ke liye us waqt tak yun dua kartey rahtey hain. jab tak (namaz padhney ke baad) wo apne musalley par betha rahe ( اللهم اغفر له,اللهم ارحمه‏ (ke aey Allaah! uski maghfirat kar. aey Allaah! is par raham kar. tum mein se wo shakhs jo sirf Namaz ki wjah se ruka hua hai. ghar janey se siwa Namaz ke aur koi cheez uske liye rukawat nahi, to uska (ye Sara waqt) Namaz hi mein shumaar hoga."
660,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke saat (7) tarah ke aadmi hongey. jinko Allah us din apne saaye mein jagah dega. jis din uske saaye ke siwa aur koi saaya na hoga. awwal insaf karne wala baadshaah, doosrey wo naujawaan jo apne rab ki ibadat mein jawaanii ki umang se masroof rahaa, tesraa aisa shakhs jiska dil har waqt masjid mein laga rehta hai, chauthey 2 aisey shakhs jo Allah ke liye aapasii mohabbat rakhtey hain aur unke milney aur juda honey ki buniyad yahi ( للهى ( (Allah ke liye muhabbat) mohabbat hai, paanchwaan wo shakhs jisey kisi baa-izzat aur Husain aurat ne ( burey irade se) bulaya lekin usne keh diya ke main Allah se darta hon, chhataa wo shakhs jisne sadqa kya, magar itney chhipe taur par ke baaein hath ko bhi khabar nahi hui ke daahiney hath ne kya kharch kya. saatwaan wo shakhs jisne tanhai mein Allah ko yad kya aur (be-saakhta) aankhon se aansu jari ho gaey."
661,"kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne koi anguthi pehni hai? aap ne farmaya ke haan! aik raat isha ki Namaz mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aadhi raat tak der ki. Namaz ke baad hamari taraf mutwajjeh huey aur farmaya, log Namaz padh kar so chukey hongey aur tum log us waqt tak Namaz hi ki haalat mein they jab tak tum Namaz ka intizar kartey rahe. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya jaisey us waqt mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki anguthi ki chamak dekh raha hun (yani Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki anguthi ki chamak ka samaan meri aankhon mein hai)."
662,Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo shakhs masjid mein subah-Shaam baar-baar haziri deta hai. Allah Taala jannat mein uski mehmani ka saman karega . wo subah-Shaam jab bhi masjid mein jaey.
663,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka guzar aik shakhs par hua (doosri sanad) imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha ke mujh se Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-Bashar ne bayan kya, kaha ke ham se Bahaz-bin-Asad ne bayan kya. kaha ke ham se Shoba ne bayan kya, kaha ke mujhey Sad bin Ibrahim ne khabar di, kaha ke maine Hafs-bin-Aasim se suna, kaha ke maine qabila Azd ke aik sahib se jinka naam Maalik-bin Buhaina (Raziallahu anhu) tha, suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki nazar aik aisey namazi par padi jo takbeer ke baad 2 rakaat Namaz padh raha tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Namaz se farigh ho gaey to log us shakhs ke ird-gird jama ho gaey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kya subah ki char rakatein padhta hai? kya subah ki char rakatein ho gain ? is hadis ki mutabiat (pairavi) ghandar aur Muaz ne Shoba se ki hai jo Malik se riwayat kartey hain. ibne- Ishaq ne Sad se, unhon-ne Hafs se, wo Abdullaah-bin-Buhaina se aur Hammad ne kaha ke hamein Sad ne Hafs ke waaste se khabar di aur wo Malik ke waasta se."
664,"ham Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir they. ham ne Namaz mein hameshgii aur uski ta'zeem ka zikr kya. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke marzul-maut mein jab Namaz ka waqt aaya aur azan di gaee to farmaya ke Abu-Bakar se kaho ke logon ko Namaz padhaaein. us waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha gaya ke Abu-Bakar badey narm dil hain. agar wo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki jagah khadey hongey to Namaz padhaanaa unke liye mushkil ho jaeygi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir wahi hukm farmaya, aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney phir wahi baat dohra di gaee. teesri martaba Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum to bilkul Yusuf ki sath wali aurton ki tarah ho. (ke dil mein kuchh hai aur zahir kuchh aur kar rahi ho ( Abu-Bakar se kaho ke wo Namaz padhaaein. aakhir Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) Namaz padhaaney ke liye tashrif laey. itney main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne marz mein kuchh kami mehsus ki aur 2 aadmiyon ka sahara lekar bahar tashrif ley gaey. maano main us waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qadmon ko dekh rahi hun ke takleef ki wjah se zameen par lakeer kartey jatey they, Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye dekh kar chaha ke peechhey hat jaaein. lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ishaare se unhein apni jagah rehney ke liye kaha, phir unke qareeb aaey aur bazu mein baith gaey. jab Aamash ne ye hadis bayan ki, unse puchha gaya ke kya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz padhai aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne aap ki iqtida (pairvi) ki aur logon ne Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki Namaz ki iqtida (pairvi) ki? Aamash ne sar ke ishaare se batlaya ke haan. Abu-Dawud Tiyalisi ne us hadis ka aik tukda Shoba se riwayat kya hai aur Shoba ne Aamash se aur abu-Muawia ne is riwayat mein ye zyada kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke baain taraf baithey. to Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) khadey ho kar Namaz padh rahe they."
665,"jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bimar ho gaey aur takleef zyada badh gaee to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni beeviyon se uski ijazat li ke bimari ke din mere ghar mein guzaarein . unhon-ne uski Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ijazat de di. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahar tashrif ley gaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qadam zameen par lakeer kar rahe they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) aur aik aur shakhs ke beech mein they (yani donon hazraat ka sahara liye huey they) Ubaidullah rawi ne bayan kya ke maine ye hadis Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan ki, to aap ne farmaya us shakhs ko bhi jantey ho, jinka naam Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne nahi liya. maine kaha ke nahi ! aap ne farmaya ke wo doosrey aadmi Ali (Raziallahu anhu) they."
666,"Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne aik thandii aur barsat ki raat mein azan di, phir yun pukar kar keh diyaa ألا صلوا في الرحال‏ ke logo! apni qiyam gaahon par hi Namaz padh lo. phir farmaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sardi w barish ki raaton mein muazzan ko hukm detey they ke wo elaan kar de ke logo apni qiyam gaahon par hi Namaz padh lo."
667,"bin Malik Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) naa-beenaa they aur wo apni qaum ke imam they. unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se arz kya ke ya Rasulullah! andherii aur sailaab ki raatein hoti hain aur main andha hon, isliye aap mere ghar mein kisi jagah Namaz padh lijiye taake main wahin apni Namaz ki jagah bana loon. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke ghar tashrif laey aur puchha ke tum kahan Namaz padhna pasand karogey. unhon-ne ghar mein aik jagah batla di aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wahan Namaz padhi."
668,"hamein aik din Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne jabke barish ki wjah se keechad ho rahi thi khutba sunaya. phir muazzan ko hukm diya aur jab wo حى على الصلاة par pahuncha to aap ne farmaya ke aaj yun pukar pukaar ( الصلاة في الرحال (ke Namaz apni qiyam gaahon par padh lo. log aik doosrey ko (hairat ki wjah se) dekhney lagey. jaisey usko unhon-ne naajaaiz samjhaa. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke aisa malum hota hai ke tum ne shayad usko bura jana hai. aisa to mujh se behtar zaat yani Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi kya tha. beshak Juma wajib hai magar maine ye pasand nahi kya ke (حى على الصلاة) keh kar tumhen bahar nikaalun (aur takleef mein mubtala karoon) aur Hammad Aasim se, wo Abdullah-bin-Haaris se, wo Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se, isi tarah riwayat kartey hain. albatta unhon-ne itna aur kaha ke Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke mujhey achchha malum nahi hua ke tumhen gunahgaar karun aur tum us haalat mein aao ke tum mitti mein ghutnon tak aalooda ho gaey ho."
669,maine Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se ( shabe-qadr ko) poochha. aap ne farmaya ke badal ka aik tukda aaya aur barsa yahan tak ke (masjid ki chhat ( tapakney lagi jo khajoor ki shakhon se banai gaee thi. phir Namaz ke liye takbeer hui. maine dekha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) keechad aur pani mein sajda kar rahe they. keechad ka nishan aap ki peshani par bhi maine dekha.
670,"Ansar mein se aik mard ne uzr pesh kya ke main aap ke sath Namaz mein Sharik nahi ho sakta aur wo mota aadmi tha. us ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye khana taiyaar kya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko apne ghar dawat di aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye aik chatai bichhaa di aur uske aik kinare ko) saaf karke) dho diya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us boriye par 2 rakatein padhin. aale-Jaarood ke aik shakhs (abdul-Hameed) ne Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke kya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) chasht ki Namaz padhtey they, to unhon-ne farmaya ke us din ke siwa aur kabhi maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko padhtey nahi dekha."
671,Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar Sham (Syria) ka khana samney rakha jaey aur idhar Namaz ke liye takbeer bhi honey lagey to pahley khana kha lo.
672,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab Sham (Syria) ka khana hazir kya jaey to maghrib ki Namaz se pahley khana kha lo aur khaney mein be maza bhi na hona chahiye aur apna khana chhod kar Namaz mein jaldi mat karo.
673,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab tum mein se kisi ka Sham ka khana taiyaar ho chuka ho aur takbeer bhi kahi ja chuki ho to pahley khana kha lo aur Namaz ke liye jaldi na karo, khaney se faraghat kar lo aur Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye khana rakh diya jata, idhar iqamat bhi ho jati lekin aap khaney se farigh honey tak Namaz mein Sharik nahi hotey they. aap imam ki qirat barabar suntey rahtey they."
674,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar tum mein se koi khana kha raha ho to jaldi na karey, balke poori tarah kha ley, halaanki Namaz khadi kyon na ho gaee ho. abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (rh)) ne kaha aur mujh se Ibrahim bin al-Munzir ne Wahab bin Usman se ye hadis bayan ki aur Wahab madni hain."
675,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bakri ki raan ka gosht kaat-kaat kar kha rahe they. itney mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz ke liye bulaey gaey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey huey aur chhuri daal di, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz padhai aur wuzu nahi kya."
676,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne ghar mein kya kiya kartey they aap ne batlaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne ghar ke kaam kaaj yani apne ghar waaliyon ki khidmat kya kartey they aur jab Namaz ka waqt hota to fauran ( kaam kaaj chhod kar) Namaz ke liye chaley jatey they.
677,"main tum logon ko Namaz padhaaunga aur meri niyat Namaz padhney ki nahi hai, mera maqsad sirf ye hai ke tumhen Namaz ka wo tariqa sikhaa dun jis tareeqe se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz padha kartey they. maine abu-Qilaba se puchha ke unhon-ne kis tarah Namaz padhi thi? unhon-ne batlaya ke hamarey Shekh (Umar-bin Salma) ki tarah. Shekh jab sajde se sar uthatey to zara baith jatey phir khadey hotey."
678,"aap ne farmaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bimar huey aur jab bimari shiddat ikhtiyar kar gaee to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se kaho ke wo logon ko Namaz padhaaein. is par Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) boliin ke wo narm-dil hain jab aap ki jagah khadey hongey to unke liye Namaz padhaanaa mushkil hoga. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir farmaya ke Abu-Bakar se kaho ke wo Namaz padhaaein. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne phir wahi baat kahi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir farmaya ke Abu-Bakar se kaho ke Namaz padhaaein, tum log Yusuf (Alaihissalam) ki aurton ki tarah (baatein banaatii) ho. aakhir Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aadmi bulaney aaya aur aap ne logon ko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zindagi mein hi Namaz padhai."
679,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni bimari mein farmaya ke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se Namaz padhaaney ke liye kaho. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke maine arz kya ke Abu-Bakar aap ki jagah khadey hongey to rotey-rotey wo ( Quran Majeed ( suna na sakengey , isliye aap umr (Raziallahu anhu) se kahey ke wo Namaz padhaaein. aap farmati thin ke maine Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) se kaha ke wo bhi kahein ke agar Abu-Bakar aap ki jagah khadey huey to rotey-rotey logon ko) Quran ( na suna sakengey . isliye umr (Raziallahu anhu) se kahey ke wo Namaz padhaaein. Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ( Ummul-Momenin aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki sahibzadi ( ne bhi isi tarah kaha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke khamosh raho. tum Yusuf (Alaihissalam) ki aurton ki tarah ho Abu-Bakar se kaho ke wo logon ko Namaz padhaaein. to phir Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se kaha, bhala mujh ko kahin tum se bhalai pahunch sakti hai?"
680,"ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke marzul-maut mein Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) Namaz padhatey they. peer ke din jab log Namaz mein saf baandhey khadey huey they, to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hujre ka parda hataaey khadey huey, hamari taraf dekh rahe they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka chehra Mubarak ( Husn w jamaal aur safaaii mein) maano kisi kitab ka waraq tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) muskuraa kar hansney lagey. hamein itni khushi hui ke khatrah ho gaya ke kahin ham sab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekhney hi mein na mashghool ho jayen aur Namaz tod dein Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ultey paon peechhey hat kar saf ke sath aa milnaa chahtey they. unhon-ne samjha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz ke liye tashrif la rahe hain, lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein ishara kya ke Namaz poori kar lo. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne parda daal diya. to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat isi din ho gaii. اناللہ و انا الیہ راجعون"
681,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (beemaarii ke dinon mein) teen din tak bahar tashrif nahi laey. un hi dinon mein aik din Namaz qaaim ki gaee Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aagey badhney ko they ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( hujra Mubarak ka ( parda uthaya . jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka chehra Mubarak dikhai diya. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke Mubarak chehre se zyada Husain manzar ham ne kabhi nahi dekha tha. (qurbaan us Husn w jamaal ke) phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ko aagey badhney ke liye ishara kya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne parda gira diya aur uske baad wafat tak koi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekhney par qaadir na ho saka.
682,"jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bimari shiddat ikhtiyar kar gaee aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Namaz ke liye kaha gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Abu-Bakar se kaho ke wo Namaz padhaaein. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne arz kya ke Abu-Bakar kachchey dil ke aadmi hain. jab wo Quran Majeed padhtey hain to bahut roney lagtey hain. lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke un hi se kaho ke Namaz padhaaein. dobara unhon-ne phir wahi uzr dohraya . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir farmaya ke unse Namaz padhaaney ke liye kaho. tum to bilkul Yusuf (Alaihissalam) ki aurton ki tarah ho. is hadis ki mutabiat (pairavi) Muhammad-bin Waleed Zubaidi aur Zohri ke bhatijey aur Ishaq bin Yahya kalbi ne Zohri se ki hai aur Aqeel aur Mamar ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Hamza bin-Abdullaah-bin-Umar se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se."
683,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni bimari mein hukm diya ke Abu-Bakar logon ko Namaz padhaaein. isliye aap logon ko Namaz padhatey they. Urwa ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik din apne aapko kuchh halka paya aur bahar tashrif laey. us waqt Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) Namaz padha rahe they. unhon-ne jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha to peechhey hatna chaha, lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ishaarey se unhein apni jagah qaaim rehney ka hukm farmaya, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ke bazu mein baith gaey Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki iqtida (pairvi) kar rahe they aur log Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki pairwi kartey they."
684,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bani Amr-bin-Auf main ( Quba mein) suleh karaaney ke liye gaey, to Namaz ka waqt aa gaya. muazzan ( Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne) Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se aa kar kaha ke kya aap Namaz padhaaeingey. mein takbeer kahun Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke haan, chunanche Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ne Namaz shuru kar di. itney main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif ley aaey to log Namaz mein they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) safon se guzar kar pehli saf mein pahunchey . logon ne aik hath ko doosrey par maara (taake Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aamad par aagah ho jaaein) lekin Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) Namaz mein kisi taraf tawajjoh nahi detey they. jab logon ne mutwaatir hath par hath maarna shuru kya to siddeeq akbar (Raziallahu anhu) mutwajjeh huey aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ishara se unhein apni jagah rehney ke liye kaha, (ke Namaz padhaaey jaao) lekin unhon-ne apne hath utha kar Allah ka shukr kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unko imamat ki izzat bakhshii, phir bhi wo peechhey hat gaey aur saf mein shamil ho gaey. isliye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aagey badh kar Namaz padhai. Namaz se farigh ho kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Abu-Bakar jab maine aapko hukm de diya tha phir aap Sabit qadam kyon na rahe Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) boley ke abu-Qahaafa ke betey (yani abu-Bakar) ki ye haisiyat na thi ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney Namaz padha sakein. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne logon ki taraf Khattab kartey huey farmaya ke ajeeb baat hai. maine dekha ke tum log kasrat se taaliyaan bajaa rahe they. (yaad rakho) agar Namaz mein koi baat pesh aa jaey to Subhan-Allah kehna chahiye jab wo ye kahega to uski taraf tawajjoh ki jaeygi aur ye taali bajanaa aurton ke liye hai."
685,ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat main apne mulk se hazir huey. ham sab ham-Umr naujawaan they. taqriban bees raatein ham aap ki khidmat mein thahrey rahe. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) badey hi raham dil they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (hamaarii ghurbat ka haal dekh kar) farmaya ke jab tum log apne gharon ko jao to apne qabeele walon ko Deen ki baatein batana aur unse Namaz padhney ke liye kehna ke falan Namaz falan waqt aur falan Namaz falan waqt padhein aur jab Namaz ka waqt ho jaey to koi aik azan de aur jo Umr mein bada ho wo imamat karaaey.
686,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (mere ghar tashrif laney ki) ijazat chahi aur maine aapko ijazat di, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke tum log apne ghar mein jis jagah pasand karo mein Namaz padh dun mein jahan chahta tha uski taraf maine ishara kya. phir aap khadey ho gaey aur ham ne aap ke peechhey saf baandh li. phir aap ne jab salam phera to ham ne bhi salam phera ."
687,"main Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur kaha, kash! ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bimari ki haalat aap ham se bayan kartin, (to achchha hota ( unhon-ne farmaya ke haan zaroor sun lo. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka marz badh gaya. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke kya logon ne Namaz padh li? ham ne kaha ji nahi ya Rasulullah ! log aap ka intizar kar rahe hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mere liye aik lagan mein pani rakh do. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke hamne pani rakh diya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne baith kar ghusl kya. phir aap uthney lagey, lekin aap behosh ho gaey. jab hosh hua to phir aap ne puchha ke kya logon ne Namaz padh li hai. ham ne kaha nahi, ya Rasulullah! log aap ka intizar kar rahe hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( phir ( farmaya ke lagan mein mere liye pani rakh do. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke ham ne phir pani rakh diya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne baith kar ghusl farmaya, phir uthney ki koshish ki lekin) dobara ( phir aap behosh ho gaey. jab hosh hua to aap ne phir yahi farmaya ke kya logon ne Namaz padh li hai. ham ne kaha ke nahi ya Rasulullah! log aapka intizar kar rahe hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir farmaya ke lagan mein pani lao aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne baith kar ghusl kya. phir uthney ki koshish ki, lekin phir aap behosh ho gaey. phir jab hosh hua to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha ke kya logon ne Namaz padh li ham ne kaha ke nahi ya Rasulullah! wo aap ka intizar kar rahe hain. log masjid mein isha ki Namaz ke liye baithey huey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka intizar kar rahe they. aakhir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aadmi bheja aur hukm farmaya ke wo Namaz padha dein. bhejey huey shakhs ne aa kar kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aapko Namaz padhaaney ke liye hukm farmaya hai. Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) badey narm dil insan they. unhon-ne umr (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke tum Namaz padhaao, lekin umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawab diya ke aap iske zyada haqdaar hain. aakhir (beemaarii) ke dinon mein Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) Namaz padhatey rahe. phir jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko mizaaj kuchh halka malum hua to 2 mardon ka sahara lekar jin mein aik Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) they Zohar ki Namaz ke liye ghar se bahar tashrif laey aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) Namaz padha rahe they, jab unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha to peechhey hatna chaha, lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ishaarey se unhein rokaa ke peechhey na hato! phir aap ne un donon mardon se farmaya ke mujhey Abu-Bakar ke bazu mein bitha do. chunanche donon ne aapko Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke bazu mein bitha diya. rawi ne kaha ke phir Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) Namaz main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki pairwi kar rahe they aur log Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki Namaz ki pairwi kar rahe they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baithey-baithey Namaz padh rahe they. Ubaidullah ne kaha ke phir main Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein gaya aur unse kaha ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bimari ke barey mein jo hadis bayan ki hai kya main wo aapko sunaun? unhon-ne farmaya ke zaroor sunao. maine ye hadis suna di. unhon-ne kisi baat ka inkar nahi kya. sirf itna kaha ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne un sahib ka naam bhi tum ko bataya jo Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath they. maine kaha nahi. aap ne farmaya wo Ali (Raziallahu anhu) they."
688,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik martaba bimari ki haalat mein mere hi ghar mein Namaz padhi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baith kar Namaz padh rahe they aur log Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey khadey ho kar padh rahe they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unko baithney ka ishara kya aur Namaz se farigh honey ke baad farmaya ke imam isliye hai ke uski pairwi ki jaey. isliye jab wo rukoo mein jaey to tum bhi rukoo mein jao aur jab wo sar uthaey to tum bhi sar uthao aur jab wo (سمع الله لمن حمده‏) kahey to tum ( ربنا ولك الحمد‏ ( kaho aur jab wo baith kar Namaz padhey to tum bhi baith kar Namaz padho .
689,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik ghodey par Sawar huey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) is par se gir padey . us se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke daain pahlu par zakhm aaey. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne koi Namaz padhi. jisey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baith kar padh rahe they. isliye ham ne bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey baith kar Namaz padhi. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farigh huey to farmaya ke imam isliye muqarrar kya gaya hai ke uski iqtida (pairvi) ki jaey. isliye jab wo khadey ho kar Namaz padhey to tum bhi khadey ho kar padho aur jab wo rukoo karey to tum bhi rukoo karo. jab wo rukoo se sar uthaey to tum bhi uthao aur jab wo (سمع الله لمن حمده‏ ) kahey to tum ( ربنا ولك الحمد‏ ( kaho aur jab wo baith kar Namaz padhey to tum bhi baith kar padho . abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ( ne kaha ke Hameedii ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke us qaul ''jab imam baith kar Namaz padhey to tum bhi baith kar padho.'' ke mutaalliq kaha hai ke ye shuruaat mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki puraanii bimari ka waqia hai. iske baad aakhiri bimari mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khud baith kar Namaz padhi thi aur log Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey khadey ho kar iqtida (pairvi) kar rahe they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us waqt logon ko baithney ki hidayat nahi farmai aur asl ye hai ke jo kaam Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka aakhiri ho usko lena chahiye aur phir jo usse aakhiri ho.
690,"jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (سمع الله لمن حمده‏) kehtey to ham mein se koi bhi us waqt tak na jhuktaa jab tak Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sajde mein na chaley jatey phir ham log sajde mein jatey. ham se abu-Nueim ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Sufiyan Sory ne, unhon-ne Abu-Ishaq se jaisey uper guzra ."
691,Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kya tum mein wo shakhs jo ( rukoo ya sajde mein) imam se pahley apna sar utha leta hai is baat se nahi darta ke kahin Allah paak iska sar gadhey ke sar ki tarah bana de ya uski sura ko gadhey ki si sura bana de.
692,jab pahley muhajireen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki hijrat se bhi pahley Quba ke maqam usba mein pahunchey to unki imamat abu-Huzaifa ke ghulam Salim (Raziallahu anhu) kya kartey they. aapko Quran Majeed sabse zyada yad tha.
693,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya (apne Hakim ki) suno aur itaat karo, chahe aik aisa habshi ( ghulam tum par) kyon na Hakim bana diya jaey jiska sar sookhey huey angoor ke barabar ho."
694,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke imam logon ko Namaz padhatey hain. to agar imam ne theek Namaz padhai to uska sawab tumhen milega aur agar ghalati ki to bhi) tumhari Namaz ka ( sawab tum ko milega aur ghalati ka wabaal un par rahega.
695,wo khud Usman ghanii (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaey. jabke baaghiyon ne unko gher rakha tha. unhon-ne kaha ke aap hi aam musalmanon ke imam hain magar aap par jo museebat hai wo aapko malum hai. in halaat mein baaghiyon ka muqarrara imam Namaz padha raha hai. ham dartey hain ke iske peechhey Namaz padh kar gunahgaar na ho jaaein. Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawab diya Namaz to jo log kaam kartey hain un kaamon mein sabse behtreen kaam hai. to wo jab achchha kaam karein tum bhi iske sath mil kar achchha kaam karo aur jab wo bura kaam karein to tum unki burai se alag raho aur Muhammad-bin Yazeed Zubaidi ne kaha ke imam Zohri ne farmaya ke ham to ye samajhtey hain ke heejdey ke peechhey Namaz na padhein. magar aisi hi laachaarii ho to aur baat hai jiske baghair koi chaara na ho.
696,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Abu-Zar se farmaya (haakim ki) sun aur itaat kar. chahe wo aik aisa habshi ghulam hi kyon na ho jiska sar munaqqey ke barabar ho.
697,"aik raat main apni khala Ummul-Momenin Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar par reh gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) isha ki Namaz ke baad jab unke ghar tashrif laey to yahan char rakaat Namaz padhi. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) so gaey phir Namaz ( tahajjud ke liye) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uthey (aur Namaz padhney lagey ( to main bhi uth kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki baain taraf khada ho gaya, lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey apni dahini taraf kar liya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne panch rakaat Namaz padhi. phir 2 rakaat ( sunnat fajr ( padh kar so gaey aur maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke kharraatey ki awaz bhi suni. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) fajr ki Namaz ke liye aaye."
698,mein aik raat Ummul-Momenin Memuna ke yahan so gaya. us raat Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bhi wahin soney ki baari thi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wuzu kya aur Namaz padhney ke liye khadey ho gaey. mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke baain taraf khada ho gaya. isliye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey pakad kar daain taraf kar diya. phir 13 rakaat ( witr samet ( Namaz padhi aur so gaey. yahan tak ke kharraatey leney lagey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab sotey to kharraatey letey they. phir muazzan aaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahar tashrif ley gaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne iske baad) fajr ki) Namaz padhi aur wuzu nahi kya. Amr ne bayan kya maine ye hadis Bukair-bin-Abdullaah ke samney bayan ki to unhon-ne farmaya ke ye hadis mujh se Kureb ne bhi bayan ki thi.
699,maine aik baar apni khala Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar raat guzari . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) raat mein Namaz padhney ke liye khadey huey to main bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Namaz mein Sharik ho gaya. main ( ghalati se) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke baain taraf khada ho gaya tha. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mera sar pakad ke daain taraf kar diya. (taake sahi taur par khada ho jaun ( .
700,"Muaz-bin-Jabal (rz), Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhtey phir wapas aa kar apni qaum ki imamat kya kartey they."
701,"Muaz-bin-Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath ( farz ( Namaz padhtey phir wapas ja kar apni qaum ke logon ko) wahi ( Namaz padhaayaa kartey they. aik baar isha mein unhon-ne sura al-Baqara shuru ki. ( muqtadiyon mein se) aik shakhs Namaz tod kar chal diya. Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) usko bura kehney lagey. ye khabar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko pahunchi (is shakhs ne ja kar Muaz ki shikayat ki) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Muaz ko farmaya to bula mein dalney wala hai, bula mein dalney waalaa, bula mein dalney wala hai, teen baar farmaya, ya yun farmaya ke to fasaadii hai, fasaadii, fasaadii. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Muaz ko hukm farmaya ke mufassal ke beech ki 2 soortein padha kare. Amr-bin-Dinar ne kaha ke mujhey yad na rahen (ke kon si Suraton ka aap ne naam liyaa.)"
702,"aik shakhs ne kaha ke ya Rasulullah! qism Allah ki mein subah ki Namaz mein falan ki wjah se der mein jata hon, kyonke wo Namaz ko bahut lamba kar detey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko nasihat ke waqt us din se zyada ( kabhi bhi) ghazab naak nahi dekha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum mein se kuchh log ye chahtey hain ke) Awam ko ibadat se ya Deen se) nafrat dila dein, khabardaar tum mein logon ko jo shakhs bhi Namaz padhaaey to halki padhaaey. kyonke namaziyon mein kamzor, boodhey aur zarurat waley sab hi qism ke log hotey hain."
703,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, jab koi tum mein se logon ko Namaz padhaaey to mukhtasar karey kyonke jamat mein zaeef bimar aur boodhey (sab hi) hotey hain, lekin akelaa padhey to jis qadr ji chahey lambi padh sakta hai."
704,"aik shakhs ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha ke ya Rasulullah! main fajr ki Namaz mein derii karke isliye Sharik hota hun ke falan sahib fajr ki Namaz bahut lambi kar detey hain. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) is qadr ghussa huey ke maine nasihat ke waqt us din se zyada ghazab naak Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko kabhi nahi dekha. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya logo ! tum mein kuchh log (namaz se logon ko) door karne ki wjah bane huey hain. isliye jo shakhs imam ho usey halki Namaz padhni chahiye isliye ke iske peechhey kamzor, boodhey aur zarurat waley sab hi hotey hain."
705,"aik shakhs pani uthaney wala 2 oont liye huey aaya, raat taareek ho chuki thi. usne Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ko Namaz padhatey huey paya. isliye apne oonton ko bitha kar (namaz mein Sharik honey ke liye) Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf badhaa. Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ne Namaz mein sura al-Baqara ya sura Nisa shuru ki. chunanche wo shakhs niyat tod kar chal diya. phir usey malum hua ke Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujh ko bura bhala kaha hai. isliye wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur Muaz ki shikayat ki, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se farmaya, Muaz ! kya tum logon ko fitne mein daltey ho. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne teen martaba ( فتان (ya ( فاتن ( farmaya :  سبح اسم ربك ‏‏‏‏ Mina والشمس وضحاها ‏‏‏‏ Mina والليل إذا يغشى( soortein ( tum ne kyon na padhein , kyonke tumharey peechhey boodhey, kamzor aur zaroorat-mand Namaz padhtey hain. Shoba ne kaha ke mera khayal hai ke ye aakhiri jumla (kyonke tumharey peechhey) hadis mein dakhil hai. Shoba ke sath uski mutabiat (pairavi) Saeed-bin-Masrooq, Misar aur Shebani ne ki hai aur Amr-bin-Diinaar, Ubaidullaah-bin -Muqsim aur abu-Zubair ne bhi us hadis ko Jaabir ke waaste se bayan kya hai ke Muaz ne isha mein sura al-Baqara padhi thi aur Shoba ke sath is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Aamash ne Maharib ke waaste se ki hai."
706,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz ko mukhtasar aur poori padhtey they.
707,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main Namaz der tak padhney ke irade se khada hota hun. lekin kisi bachchey ke roney ki awaz sun kar Namaz ko halki kar deta hun, kyonke uski maan ko (jo Namaz mein Sharik hogi) takleef mein daalnaa bura samajhta hun. Waleed-bin-Muslim ke sath is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) bishr-bin-bakr, Baqiiya-bin-Waleed aur ibne-Mubarak ne Auzai ke waaste se ki hai."
708,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se zyada halki lekin kaamil Namaz maine kisi imam ke peechhey kabhi nahi padhi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka ye haal tha ke agar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bachchey ke roney ki awaz sun letey to us khayal se ke uski maan kahin pareshani mein na mubtala ho jaey Namaz mukhtasar kar detey.
709,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya main Namaz shuru kar deta hun. irada ye hota hai ke Namaz lambi karun lekin bachchey ke roney ki awaz sun kar mukhtasar kar deta hun kyonke mujhey malum hai ke maa ke dil par bachchey ke roney se kaisi chot padtii hai.
710,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main Namaz ki niyat baandhtaa hon, irada ye hota hai ke Namaz ko lamba karunga, lekin bachchey ke roney ki awaz sun kar mukhtasar kar deta hun kyonke main us dard ko samajhta hun jo bachchey ke roney ki wjah se maan ko ho jata hai. aur Moosaa-bin-Ismaaeel ne kaha ham se Aban bin Yazeed ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Qatada ne, kaha ham se Anas ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se yahi hadis bayan ki."
711,"Muaz (rz), Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhtey phir wapas aa kar apni qaum ko Namaz padhatey they."
712,aap ne batlaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke maut ke marz mein Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) Namaz ki itlaa dene ke liye haazire-khidmat huey. aap ne farmaya ke Abu-Bakar se Namaz padhaaney ke liye kaho. maine arz kya ke Abu-Bakar kachchey dil ke aadmi hain agar aap ki jagah khadey hongey to ro dengey aur qirat na kar sakengey . aap ne farmaya ke Abu-Bakar se kaho wo Namaz padhaaein. maine wahi uzr phir dohraayaa. phir aap ne teesri ya chothi martaba farmaya ke tum log to bilkul Yusuf (Alaihissalam) ki aurton ki tarah ho Abu-Bakar se kaho ke wo Namaz padhaaein. khair Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Namaz shuru kara di. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (apnaa mizaaj zara halka pa kar) 2 aadmiyon ka sahara liye huey bahar tashrif laey. maano meri nazron ke samney wo manzar hai ke aap ke qadam zameen par rakh rahe they Abu-Bakar aapko dekh kar peechhey hatney lagey. lekin aap ne ishaare se unhein Namaz padhaaney ke liye kaha Abu-Bakar peechhey hat gaey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke bazu mein baithey Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) logon ko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki takbeer suna rahe they. Abdullaah-bin-Daawood ke sath us hadis ko muhaazir ne bhi Aamash se riwayat kya hai.
713,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) zyada bimar ho gaey they, to Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Namaz ki khabar dene aaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Abu-Bakar se Namaz padhaaney ke liye kaho. maine kaha ke ya Rasulullah! Abu-Bakar aik narm dil aadmi hain aur jab bhi wo aap ki jagah khadey hongey logon ko (shiddat giryaa ki wjah se) awaz nahi suna sakengey. isliye agar umr (Raziallahu anhu) se kehtey to behtar tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Abu-Bakar se Namaz padhaaney ke liye kaho. phir maine Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) se kaha ke tum kaho ke Abu-Bakar narm dil aadmi hain aur agar aap ki jagah khadey huey to logon ko apni awaz nahi suna sakengey . isliye agar umr se kahein to behtar hoga. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum log Yusuf (Alaihissalam) ki aurton se kam nahi ho Abu-Bakar se kaho ke Namaz padhaaein. jab Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) Namaz padhaaney lagey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne marz mein kuchh halkaapan mehsus farmaya aur 2 aadmiyon ka sahara lekar khadey ho gaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paon zameen par nishan kar rahe they. is tarah chal kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) masjid mein dakhil huey. jab Abu-Bakar ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aahat paai to peechhey hatney lagey isliye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ishaare se rokaa phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke baain taraf baith gaey to Abu-Bakar khadey hokar Namaz padh rahe they. aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baith kar Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki iqtida (pairvi) kar rahe they aur log Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki iqtidaa."
714,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (zuhar ki Namaz mein) 2 rakaat padh kar Namaz khatm kar di to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se zul-yadain ne kaha ke ya Rasulullah! kya Namaz kam ho gaee hai ya aap bhool gaey hain? is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (aur logon ki taraf dekh kar) puchha kya zul-yadain sahi kehtey hain? logon ne kaha ke haan! phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uthey aur dusri 2 rakatein bhi padhein. phir salam pheraa. phir takbeer kahi aur sajda kya pahley ki tarah ya us se kuchh lamba sajda.
715,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (eik martaba ( Zohar ki sirf 2 hi rakatein padhaaiin (aur bhool se salam pher diyaa) phir kaha gaya ke aap ne sirf 2 hi rakatein padhi hain. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne 2 rakatein aur padhein phir salam pheraa. phir 2 sajdey kiye.
716,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne maut ke marz mein farmaya ke Abu-Bakar se logon ko Namaz padhaaney ke liye kaho. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain ke maine kaha ke Abu-Bakar agar aap ki jagah khadey huey to roney ki wjah se logon ko apni awaz na suna sakengey. isliye aap umr (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaiye ke wo Namaz padhaaein. aap ne phir farmaya ke nahi Abu-Bakar hi se Namaz padhaaney ke liye kaho. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke maine Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) se kaha ke tum bhi to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se arz karo ke agar Abu-Bakar aap ki jagah khadey huey to aapko yad karke giryaa w zaarii ki wjah se logon ko Quran na suna sakengey . isliye umr (Raziallahu anhu) se kahey ke wo Namaz padhaaein. Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ne bhi keh diya. is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, bas chup raho, tum log Yusuf (Alaihissalam) se kisi tarah kam nahi ho Abu-Bakar se kaho ke wo Namaz padhaaiin. baad mein Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se kaha, bhala mujh ko tum se kahin bhalai honii hai."
717,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, Namaz main apni safon ko barabar kar lo, nahi to Allah Taala tumhara munh ulat dega."
718,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, safein seedhi kar lo. main tumhen apni peeth ke peechhey se dekh raha hun."
719,Namaz ke liye takbeer kahi gaee to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apna munh hamari taraf kya aur farmaya ke apni safein barabar kar lo aur mil kar khadey ho jao. main tum ko apni peeth ke peechhey se bhi dekhta rehta hun.
720,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke doobney waale, pet ki bimari mein marney waale, taaoon mein marney waley aur dab kar marney waley Shahid hain."
721,agar log jaan lein jo sawab Namaz ke liye jaldi aaney mein hai to aik doosrey se aagey badhiin aur agar isha aur subah ki Namaz ke sawab ko jaan lein to uske liye zaroor aaein . chahe peeth ke bal aana padey aur agar pehli saf ke sawab ko jaan lein to uske liye Qura andazi karein.
722,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke imam isliye hota hai taake uski pairwi ki jaey, isliye tum us se ikhtilaf na karo. jab wo rukoo karey to tum bhi rukoo karo aur jab wo (سمع الله لمن حمده) kahey to tum ( ربنا لك الحمد‏ ( kaho aur jab wo sajda karey to tum bhi sajda karo aur jab wo baith kar Namaz padhey to tum sab bhi baith kar padho aur Namaz mein safain barabar rakho, kyonke Namaz ka Husn safon ke barabar rakhney mein hai."
723,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke safain barabar rakho kyonke safon ka barabar rakhna Namaz ke qaaim karne mein dakhil hai.
724,"jab wo ( Basra se) Madina aaey, to aap se puchha gaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahade-mubaarak aur hamarey us daur mein aap ne kya farq paya. farmaya ke aur to koi baat nahi sirf log safain barabar nahi kartey aur Aqba-bin-Ubaid ne Basheer-bin-Yasaar se yun riwayat kya ke Anas (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey paas Madina tashrif laey. phir yahi hadis bayan ki."
725,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, safain barabar kar lo. main tumhen apne peechhey se bhi dekhta rehta hon aur ham mein se har shakhs ye karta ke (saff mein) apna kandhaa apne sathi ke kandhey se aur apna qadam (paaun) iske qadam ( paon ( se mila deta tha."
726,aik raat maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath (aap ke ghar mein tahajjud ki) Namaz padhi. mein aap ke baain taraf khada ho gaya. isliye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne peechhey se mera sar pakad kar mujhey apne daain taraf kar diya. phir Namaz padhi aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) so gaey jab muazzan (namaz ki itlaa dene ( aaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz padhaaney ke liye khadey huey aur wuzu nahi kya.
727,"maine aur aik yateem ladkey (Zameera-bin-abii-Zameera) ne jo hamarey ghar mein maujood tha, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey Namaz padhi aur meri walida Umme-Sulaim hamarey peechhey thin."
728,mein aik raat Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke baain taraf (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ghar mein) Namaz ( tahajjud ( padhney ke liye khada ho gaya. isliye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mera sar ya bazu pakad kar mujh ko apni daain taraf khada kar diya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne hath se ishara kya tha ke peechhey se ghoom aao.
729,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) raat main apne hujre ke andar ( tahajjud ki) Namaz padhtey they. hujrey ki diwarein past thin isliye logon ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekh liya aur kuchh log Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki iqtida (pairvi) mein Namaz ke liye khadey ho gaey. subah ke waqt logon ne iska zikr dusron se kya. phir jab dusri raat Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey huey to kuchh log Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki iqtida (pairvi) mein us raat bhi khadey ho gaey. ye sura 2 ya teen raat tak rahi. iske baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baith rahe aur Namaz ke maqam par tashrif nahi laey. phir subah ke waqt logon ne iska zikr kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main dara ke kahin raat ki Namaz ( tahajjud ( tum par farz na ho jaey. (is khayal se maine yahan ka aana naagha kar diyaa).
730,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aik chatai thi. jisey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) din mein bichhaatey they aur raat mein iska parda kar letey they. phir chand log Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas khadey huey ya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf jhukey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey Namaz padhney lagey.
731,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ramazan mein aik hujra bana liya ya ot ( parda ( Basar-bin-Saeed ne kaha, main samajhta hun wo boriye ka tha. aap ne kai raat usmein Namaz padhi. sahaba mein se kuchh hazraat ne un raaton mein aap ki iqtida (pairvi) ki. jab aapko iska ilm hua to aap ne baith rehna shuru kya (namaz rok rakhii) phir baraamad huey aur farmaya tum ne jo kya wo mujh ko malum hai, lekin logo ! tum apne gharon mein Namaz padhtey raho kyonke behtar Namaz aadmi ki wahi hai jo uske ghar mein ho. magar farz Namaz (masjid mein padhni zaroori hai) aur Affaan-bin-Muslim ne kaha ke ham se Wuhaib ne bayan kya, kaha ke ham se Musa-bin-Aqba ne bayan kya, kaha ke maine abu-Nazar-ibn-abii-Umayya se suna, wo Basar-bin-Saeed se riwayat kartey they, wo zaid-bin-Saabit se, wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se."
732,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik ghodey par Sawar huey aur) gir janey ki wjah se) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke daaein pahlu mein zakhm aa gaey. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne batlaya ke us din hamein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik Namaz padhai, chunkey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baithey huey they, isliye ham ne bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey baith kar Namaz padhi. phir salam ke baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke imam isliye hai ke uski pairwi ki jaey. isliye jab wo khadey ho kar Namaz padhey to tum bhi khadey ho kar padho aur jab wo rukoo karey to tum bhi rukoo karo aur jab wo sar uthaey to tum bhi uthao aur jab wo sajda karey to tum bhi karo aur jab wo (سمع الله لمن حمده) kahey to tum ( ربنا ولك الحمد ( kaho."
733,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghodey se gir gaey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) zakhmi ho gaey, isliye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne baith kar Namaz padhi aur ham ne bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki iqtida (pairvi) mein baith kar Namaz padhi. phir Namaz padh kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke imam isliye hai ke uski pairwi ki jaey. isliye jab wo takbeer kahey to tum bhi takbeer kaho. jab wo rukoo karey to tum bhi rukoo karo. jab wo sar uthey to tum bhi uthao aur jab wo ( سمع الله لمن حمده ( kahey to tum ( ربنا لك الحمد (aur jab wo sajda karey to tum bhi karo."
734,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, imam isliye hai ke uski pairwi ki jaey, isliye jab wo takbeer kahey to tum bhi takbeer kaho. jab wo rukoo karey to tum bhi rukoo karo aur jab wo ( سمع الله لمن حمده ( kahey to tum ( ربنا ولك الحمد (aur jab wo sajda karey to tum bhi sajda karo aur jab wo baith kar Namaz padhey to tum sab bhi baith kar Namaz padho."
